summary: EXPLODING SUNROOF. AS I WAS DRIVING DOWN A BUSY HIGHWAY, I HEARD A LOUD EXPLOSION FROM THE TOP IF MY VEHICLE. I THEN HEARD LITTLE SHATTERS, OF WHAT I KNOW NOW, WAS TEMPERED GLASS FALLING ON MY SUNROOF SHADE. WHEN IT WAS SAFE, I PULLED OVER AND THERE WAS A HUGE WHILE IN THE MIDDLE OF MY SUNROOF.
